dct_title_s: Asia, cum omnibus imperiis, provinciis, statibus et insulis
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Text in cartouche in upper right: Lector benevole ... Seutter was awarded the title of Imperial Geographer in 1731; the business passed to his son-in-law, Tobias Conrad Lotter, in 1760; cf. Tooley's dict. of mapmakers.
